'''Fogblaster''' was a type of [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage. [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] hated fogblasters, and only ordered them when she wanted a drink to nurse for some time.

[[Ben Skywalker]] was instructed to order a Sapphire Fogblaster at the [[Big Boom]] [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] on [[Nova Station]] after breaking out of a [[Galactic Alliance Guard|GAG]] prison. Shortly after ordering one, the twin [[Hapan Security]] agents [[Trista Zel|Trista]] and [[Taryn Zel]] recognized the fogblaster and extracted Ben from Nova Station.

